title: Bacterial Cell Illustration
description: An illustration of a bacterial cell, featuring a rounded shape with a thick outer membrane and hair-like structures (flagella) protruding from its surface. Inside, there are strands of genetic material and a gel-like cytoplasm, depicted in vibrant colors.

title: Cell Division Stages
description: An illustration depicting three stages of cell division, featuring circular shapes with a purple interior and green outlines, set against a pink background.

title: Seaweed Salad
description: A vibrant green seaweed salad, featuring strands of seaweed that are glossy and slightly curled. The salad appears fresh and is likely garnished with small yellow seeds, adding texture and color.

title: Simple Geometric Shape
description: A minimalist black and white illustration featuring a simple geometric shape resembling a corner or an L-shape.
